{"tid":2461077,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鐘翰林案 保釋被拒","createTime":"2021-03-25T08:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T08:19:45.000Z","uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4411f4901dba601fafb3f112ba6ef746143bf68b","tid":2461077,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:15:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2420841024641862/posts/4107382142654400/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2420841024641862%2Fposts%2F4107382142654400%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FsSEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=17c6e704\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2420841024641862/posts/4107382142654400/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【鍾翰林案 保釋被拒】<br />\n<br />\n前學生動源鐘翰林被控國安法中「分裂國家」、「串謀發布煽動性刊物」及兩項洗黑錢，共四項控罪。案件由國安法制定法官、區域法官胡雅文處理。鍾翰林今在區域法院否認所有控罪。 <br />\n<br />\n由於早前鐘翰林因被裁定非法集結以及侮辱國旗罪罪成，在3月1日已經刑滿，現階段只因本案需還柙。辯方申請保釋，但遭駁回。 <br />\n<br />\n案件將會六月一日在去區域法院再提堂，屆時將會擬定審訊日期和長度，另在八月十六日早上進行審前覆核，聆訊將會以中文進行。<br />\n<br />\n奧地利領事館亦有派代表到庭聽訊，代表表示將繼續留意鍾的案件。<br />\n<br />\n採訪 /  記者 王紀堯"},{"pid":"659ba8f70a4e3f75deff8b07336c3b0703bf4f17","tid":2461077,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1347ceff1713eecbe474c4e4a6ed6024084e5e4f","tid":2461077,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"659ba8f70a4e3f75deff8b07336c3b0703bf4f17","tid":2461077,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}